Class DefaultNavigatorModelComponent

  • java.lang.Object

    TreeNavigatorComponent, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable
    public final class DefaultNavigatorModelComponent
extends NavigatorComponent
implements TreeNavigatorComponent
    The default NavigatorComponent displayed in the Navigator for models, this component contains the familiar navigator tree used to view components, categories, etc.
